Phew!

294
00:53:33,627 --> 00:53:34,921
Jesus! Um...

295
00:53:35,004 --> 00:53:37,757
- What the hell happened here?
- I don't know. Um...

296
00:53:37,841 --> 00:53:39,258
I responded to a call.

297
00:53:39,341 --> 00:53:42,302
