309
00:54:05,744 --> 00:54:08,121
but I just started this job,
and when I got here...

310
00:54:08,204 --> 00:54:11,040
- Are you police?
- Deputy. Just barely, though.

311
00:54:12,374 --> 00:54:14,753
I can call the Sheriff,
if I can just use your...?

312
00:54:17,964 --> 00:54:18,965
Here you go.

