316
00:54:37,192 --> 00:54:39,651
No one else here,
but a neighbour just showed up.

317
00:54:40,945 --> 00:54:42,279
Yeah. OK.

318
00:54:43,572 --> 00:54:44,573
See you soon.

319
00:54:46,366 --> 00:54:47,493
Hey, did you see that?

320
00:54:52,539 --> 00:54:53,875
