well, just about your size, actually.

329
00:55:20,944 --> 00:55:22,028
You know, like a jock.

330
00:55:22,111 --> 00:55:23,238
Linebacker type.

331
00:55:24,197 --> 00:55:25,197
Scary guy.

332
00:55:27,158 --> 00:55:28,201
