385
00:59:06,710 --> 00:59:09,464
Shh! It's OK. It's OK. It's OK.

386
00:59:17,596 --> 00:59:18,597
[grunting]

387
00:59:28,274 --> 00:59:29,649
[intruder chokes]

388
00:59:31,610 --> 00:59:32,610
