426
01:02:28,036 --> 01:02:30,248
<i>Sooner or later, he is coming in here.</i>

427
01:02:30,331 --> 01:02:31,582
<i>He knows I am bleeding out.</i>

428
01:02:31,666 --> 01:02:33,833
